the things that are high-level

00:09:28.920 --> 00:09:33.640
so we can explain the magic
that's in the platform

00:09:33.640 --> 00:09:39.140
so that we can tweak it
slightly and innovate outside.

00:09:39.140 --> 00:09:40.537
