00:19:34.620 --> 00:19:36.370
[INAUDIBLE] would think
the same way, too.

00:19:36.370 --> 00:19:38.260
So that lack of
trust-- that means

00:19:38.260 --> 00:19:41.310
that outside players like Adobe
and Intel-- when they come in,

00:19:41.310 --> 00:19:43.980
they basically don't
have any leg to stand on

00:19:43.980 --> 00:19:47.100
and they will have to depend
