00:36:13.280 --> 00:36:14.040
[INAUDIBLE] today.

00:36:14.040 --> 00:36:16.950
ADRIAN BATEMAN: I just want to
give a note of caution, though.

00:36:16.950 --> 00:36:20.930
I'm certainly in
favor of us exploring

00:36:20.930 --> 00:36:24.860
