that it's always the case

00:36:55.640 --> 00:36:57.220
that a black box is a bad thing.

00:36:57.220 --> 00:36:58.490
I think sometimes

00:36:58.490 --> 00:37:00.310
LYZA GARDNER: It's a
place for abstraction.

00:37:00.310 --> 00:37:01.185
ADRIAN BATEMAN: Yeah.

00:37:01.185 --> 00:37:04.190
It allows us to innovate
in ways which we might not

00:37:04.190 --> 00:37:05.822
be able to do if we
expose everything.

