00:44:01.620 --> 00:44:05.110
And so job isn't done if
you only do the first part,

00:44:05.110 --> 00:44:08.160
and we've for a very long
time settled on the notion

00:44:08.160 --> 00:44:09.670
that we might be
binding ourselves

00:44:09.670 --> 00:44:12.320
into some sort of
particular architecture

00:44:12.320 --> 00:44:14.269
if we expose it as a way
of not doing job two.

00:44:14.269 --> 00:44:16.560
And I wanted to push back on
