As long as you can figure out
ways to go fast when you're not

00:44:31.380 --> 00:44:34.000
being asked to do a very
specific thing, then

00:44:34.000 --> 00:44:36.167
in the general case you can
still accelerate things.

00:44:36.167 --> 00:44:37.166
LYZA GARDNER: All right.

