00:55:00.440 --> 00:55:02.320
to the standards process?

00:55:02.320 --> 00:55:04.380
ADRIAN BATEMAN: Yeah, every API.

00:55:04.380 --> 00:55:05.720
Every single one.

00:55:05.720 --> 00:55:07.180
