If we can find a
happy medium for how

00:55:43.500 --> 00:55:47.570
we can take in
proposals for new ideas

00:55:47.570 --> 00:55:51.180
and not mix them up with the
things which are stabilizing,

00:55:51.180 --> 00:55:52.980
and not mix them up
