01:14:28.010 --> 01:14:31.960
I spent eight years working
as an executive and a product

01:14:31.960 --> 01:14:35.209
developer in Silicon Valley,
and then I moved to Oakland

01:14:35.209 --> 01:14:36.750
because it was kind
of like Brooklyn,

01:14:36.750 --> 01:14:38.580
where I had lived
for many years.

01:14:38.580 --> 01:14:41.300
