who see themselves as very

01:16:07.520 --> 01:16:11.860
isolated, very shut out, very
not able to work in tech--

01:16:11.860 --> 01:16:14.860
they wouldn't fit in-- and
light a fire of hope that's

01:16:14.860 --> 01:16:17.800
really connected to building
relationships by meeting

01:16:17.800 --> 01:16:20.880
people, working in the field,
having mentors, visiting

01:16:20.880 --> 01:16:22.120
tech companies.

01:16:22.120 --> 01:16:24.370
